	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Heda, <tag a="110" b="3" />!<delay8 /> Ich hab schon nach dir gesucht.<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Du wolltest doch <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x11 0xcd00 0xa 0x65 0x69 0x6e 0x65 0x6e 0x8 0x65 0x69 0x6e 0x65 0x6 0x65 0x69 0x6e" /> <tag a="50" b="23" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />, oder?<10_4 /> <anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Tja, rate mal, was ich hier hab.</message>
